short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Nfig | AI Agent to automate repetitive tasks.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Nfig.ai is an innovative AI-powered browser assistant designed to revolutionise the way users interact with the web. This intelligent co-pilot seamlessly improves your browsing experience, offering a wide range of capabilities to streamline and enhance your online activities.

It can help you with finding any web content, ordering food on doordash, shopping on on amazon, post on social media like Twitter, LinkedIn & Messenger, fill out any forms & give shopping opinions, and can be triggered by as simply as opening a new tab page.
